base_revision.description:
The target's promotable-config revision the plan captured
(`base_revision`). Apply proceeds only if the target still carries it;
otherwise it fails with a drift error and changes nothing.

UpdateUserRequest.description:
The body to update a user (issue #52), applied as an RFC 7396 JSON Merge Patch
over the mutable profile. Only the standard-claim document is updatable here;
the lifecycle state and external id have their own explicit operations.
